data.description: This property is located on the south side of St. James.  Featuring a spacious kitchen with lots of oak cabinets, eating area, formal dining room with built-in hutches, nice sized living room, full bath.  Newer one-story addition with master bedroom with lots of closets, family room on first floor with patio doors to very nice backyard, partially finished basement with fireplace, 3/4 bath.  Second floor has two very nice sized bedrooms, closets, renovated 3/4 bath.  Energy efficient Lennox furnace with central a/c, 150-amp CB, thermopane windows, large 2+ stall garage and separate shop area.  Must see to appreciate!
